- info: 
  Encrypt Any File And Write Result into filename.enc

  Warning: Do Not Change The Encrypted File Extension (.enc) Or You will face errors While Decrypting The File

- usage:
            File Name Or Path
           ____________________
  encrypt         <arg>
                 -------
                    1

  encrypt <file name>

- examples:

1-)  encrypt my_notes.txt  (Will Result a new file named my_notes.txt.enc)

2-)  encrypt /etc/passwd  (Will Result a new file in the /etc directory /etc/passwd.enc)

3-)  encrypt a.out

4-)  encrypt /bin/ls (Will Result a new file in the /bin directory /bin/ls.enc)
